Raphaël Personnaz https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rapha%C3%ABl_Personnaz 0 Raphaël Personnaz (born 23 July 1981) is a French actor. He has appeared in more than fifty films since 1998. He was awarded the Prix Patrick Dewaere in 2013. Raphaël_Personnaz ( born 23_July_1981 ) is a_French_actor . He has_appeared in more_than_fifty_films since 1998 .
